      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，是想用左右布局（LR）来展示流程对吧？我注意到您提到了\"正负反馈\"，是用实线箭头配合正负号来表示吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "arrow",
        "+",
        "-"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，|+|表示正向促进，|-|表示负向抑制。先从左边放交易者节点，右边展开两个交易对A和B。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "traders",
        "tradeA",
        "tradeB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我把traders放在最左，tradeA和tradeB并列在右侧，都用tr样式类保持视觉统一。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "traders",
        "tradeA",
        "tradeB",
        "tr"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "接下来需要体现代币数量的变化。每个交易对会消耗一种代币、获得另一种代币——Trade A用代币A换B，Trade B反过来。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tradeA",
        "tradeB",
        "numA",
        "numB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以tradeA到numA是负向（消耗），到numB是正向（获得）；tradeB则相反？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "tradeA",
        "tradeB",
        "numA",
        "numB"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。然后代币数量增加会正向反馈给交易者，表示他们的持仓价值上升。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "numA",
        "numB",
        "traders"
